"eBay Moderation: IN (Exports)","Arvind Dhanasekaran","2025-12-29","Critical","Weekly moderation and reporting activities continued as planned. In parallel, a persistent platform-level access issue on the Aurora Export Community was actively tracked and coordinated with Khoros/IgniteTech stakeholders. The issue manifests as repeated human-verification prompts, login/logout loop failures, and intermittent loss of analytics visibility, which has required frequent cache and cookie resets to regain access. The issue has been escalated multiple times through official support channels and is now being handled as a P0 by the Technical Account Manager, with Engineering involvement.","This is a platform-level authentication and session-handling issue, outside the moderation team’s direct control. The problem is recurring despite temporary recoveries and is impacting not only moderation workflows but also community managers on the customer side, who are unable to reliably access analytics and community features. There is also concern that this may be contributing to reduced community traffic and engagement. Resolution is fully dependent on Engineering investigation and fixes.","Continue close coordination with the Technical Account Manager and Account Owner to push for resolution of the P0 issue. Keep the customer informed of progress and workarounds where possible, while maintaining regular moderation and reporting delivery in parallel. Escalate further if the issue continues to impact community operations.","1/6/2026, 5:23:56 PM","Arvind Dhanasekaran"
